    <briefdescription>
<para>This block displays a plot of a value with a given interval in milliseconds. label_y represents the identifier (symbol) of the data. The y axis is scaled with axis_y. range_time gives the shown range of the x axis in seconds. label is an additional label for the title. </para>
    </briefdescription>
